    "body": "### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.5.0\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nYes, VIM v8.0.1365\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nMacOS Mojave 10.14.6\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nIterm2 3.4.8 (also tested in Terminal.app 2.9.5)\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nhomebrew\n\n### How to reproduce the issue\n\nnvim -u NONE\r\n:edit foo\r\n:set nowrap\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nOn sidescroll, NVIM scrolls horizontally with nowrap\n\n### Actual behavior\n\nOn sidescroll, NVIM does nothing",
